The New York Mets hired former
Toronto Blue Jays General Manager J.P. Ricciardi as special
assistant to Sandy Alderson, the Major League Baseball team said
in a statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jay Beberman at 
 jbeberman@bloomberg.net  